<h1>Admin Dashboard</h1>

<div class="alert alert-info">
  <strong>Welcome, <%= current_user.first_name %>!</strong>
  This is your admin dashboard where you can manage users and view quotes.
</div>

<h2>Manage Users</h2>
<p>
  Here you can view, edit, or delete user accounts.
</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <%= link_to 'View All Users', users_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= link_to 'Create New User', new_user_path, class: "btn btn-success" %>
  </li>
</ul>

<h2>Manage Quotes</h2>
<p>
  Here you can manage quotes contributed by users.
</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <%= link_to 'View All Quotes', quotes_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= link_to 'Add New Quote', new_quote_path, class: "btn btn-success" %>
  </li>
</ul>

<h2>Other Admin Functions</h2>
<p>
  This section can be expanded with more admin functionalities as needed.
</p>
